23
00:03:18,260 --> 00:03:19,980
Why do you still take me here?

24
00:03:21,580 --> 00:03:22,740
With my company,

25
00:03:23,180 --> 00:03:24,660
they can't hurt you!

26
00:03:25,300 --> 00:03:27,260
You are Aranya here.

27
00:03:28,180 --> 00:03:30,020
It was with their care that you grew up!

28
00:03:30,820 --> 00:03:32,460
Since Aranya was born,

29
00:03:33,420 --> 00:03:34,700
she had been staying there.

30
00:03:36,060 --> 00:03:37,420
Maybe they still know you.

31
00:03:38,260 --> 00:03:40,100
Even if they know me, I dare not go inside.

32
00:03:40,740 --> 00:03:42,660
Why do you take me here?

33
00:03:43,140 --> 00:03:44,140
Do you still remember,

34
00:03:44,460 --> 00:03:45,540
in the Fanyin Valley,

35
00:03:45,980 --> 00:03:47,260
it was through this Python Formation that

36
00:03:47,420 --> 00:03:48,860
we entered the Dream of Aranya by accident?

37
00:03:50,820 --> 00:03:51,580
I'm wondering

38
00:03:53,180 --> 00:03:55,820
if there is something secret in the Python Formation.

39
00:04:00,860 --> 00:04:01,460
Really?

40
00:04:01,980 --> 00:04:03,380
Can we get out?

41
00:04:04,780 --> 00:04:06,900
After all, the Python Formation was made artificially,

42
00:04:07,420 --> 00:04:08,860
which is different from the real one.

43
00:04:09,660 --> 00:04:10,620
After you entered the dream,

44
00:04:10,860 --> 00:04:12,020
I heard

45
00:04:12,460 --> 00:04:13,660
the Dream of Aranya

46
00:04:14,260 --> 00:04:15,580
accidentally drifted to

47
00:04:15,580 --> 00:04:17,340
the Python Formation near the Jieyou Spring.

48
00:04:19,100 --> 00:04:20,820
According to my observation,

49
00:04:20,980 --> 00:04:21,940
the Dream of Aranya

50
00:04:22,060 --> 00:04:23,700
is similar to the Ten-evil Lotus Land,

51
00:04:24,260 --> 00:04:25,700
both of which are magic wards.

52
00:04:26,460 --> 00:04:28,380
Since you could easily

53
00:04:28,500 --> 00:04:30,500
break the Ten-evil Lotus Land to get out,

54
00:04:30,700 --> 00:04:32,980
it may not be difficult to get out
of the Dream of Aranya, either.

55
00:04:33,260 --> 00:04:33,660
Right?

56
00:04:36,300 --> 00:04:37,260
As for this...

57
00:04:38,420 --> 00:04:39,740
Unless you are injured.

58
00:04:43,060 --> 00:04:43,780
So

59
00:04:43,900 --> 00:04:45,820
