60
00:04:47,060 --> 00:04:47,500
Your Majesty.

61
00:04:47,700 --> 00:04:48,700
Tell me the truth.

62
00:04:49,540 --> 00:04:51,540
I don't think

63
00:04:51,620 --> 00:04:53,020
