64
00:04:53,340 --> 00:04:54,940
How did you get injured?

65
00:05:03,340 --> 00:05:05,580
In order to enter the Dream of Aranya with you

66
00:05:05,780 --> 00:05:07,380
without breaking it,

67
00:05:08,220 --> 00:05:10,300
