85
00:06:06,660 --> 00:06:08,020
I'm not sure that I can avoid hurting you

86
00:06:08,140 --> 00:06:10,780
while using magic power to break it.

87
00:06:11,380 --> 00:06:12,100
So

88
00:06:13,300 --> 00:06:14,860
let's try to find out

89
00:06:15,420 --> 00:06:16,540
something strange of the Python Formation.

90
00:06:52,100 --> 00:06:52,660
How is it?

91
00:06:52,940 --> 00:06:53,580
How?

92
00:06:59,180 --> 00:07:00,620
If we want to get out of the Python Formation

93
00:07:00,620 --> 00:07:01,740
and the Dream of Aranya,

94
00:07:03,620 --> 00:07:05,340
we have to take the course of Aranya's life

95
00:07:05,340 --> 00:07:06,140
