98
00:07:16,580 --> 00:07:18,020
Moye once told me that

99
00:07:18,340 --> 00:07:19,740
he left the Fanyin Valley

100
00:07:19,900 --> 00:07:20,940
after the event of Quanyin Beast happened.

101
00:07:21,100 --> 00:07:22,780
Shen Ye and Aranya stayed in the mansion.

102
00:07:23,140 --> 00:07:24,620
Although they didn't show their heart to each other,

103
00:07:24,740 --> 00:07:26,460
they were deeply attracted to each other

104
00:07:26,620 --> 00:07:27,740
with a sweet life.

105
00:07:28,380 --> 00:07:28,940
Really?

106
00:07:31,620 --> 00:07:32,700
If I have to

107
00:07:32,700 --> 00:07:34,860
take the life course of Aranya,

108
00:07:35,780 --> 00:07:36,900
then I have to...

109
00:07:37,020 --> 00:07:38,340
Naturally, you can't do that.

110
00:07:40,900 --> 00:07:42,180
Then just do as what we said before.

111
00:07:42,500 --> 00:07:44,180
I can keep a distance with Shen Ye.

112
00:07:45,340 --> 00:07:46,820
Moye also told me that

113
00:07:47,300 --> 00:07:50,060
I didn't need to care much about the details.

114
00:07:50,260 --> 00:07:51,780
When I have to make any choices for the big events,

115
00:07:51,900 --> 00:07:53,900
if I do the same as Aranya did, that's OK.

116
00:07:54,740 --> 00:07:56,580
Did Su Moye tell you

117
00:07:56,700 --> 00:07:58,940
what the next big event was?

118
00:08:01,020 --> 00:08:02,020
His Majesty's demise.

119
00:08:02,580 --> 00:08:04,460
It seems to be a long time before that.

120
00:08:07,100 --> 00:08:07,980
Let's go back now.

121
00:08:29,860 --> 00:08:31,860
Having walked for a whole day, I even have blisters on my feet.

122
00:08:32,180 --> 00:08:32,780
Really?

123
00:08:33,980 --> 00:08:35,140
I will give you a foot massage.

124
00:08:41,220 --> 00:08:41,780
What's wrong?

125
00:08:47,340 --> 00:08:47,820
It's nothing.

126
00:08:50,380 --> 00:08:51,180
You can go back first.

127
00:08:51,980 --> 00:08:53,260
What are you going to do?

128
00:08:54,100 --> 00:08:54,700
Don't worry.

129
00:08:55,060 --> 00:08:56,260
I'll be back soon.

130
00:09:23,220 --> 00:09:24,900
