132
00:09:48,100 --> 00:09:50,100
Was it necessary for you to behave so secretly?

133
00:09:53,100 --> 00:09:54,660
There isn't cotton rose here.

134
00:09:55,220 --> 00:09:56,980
So I can't make cotton rose ointment.

135
00:09:58,140 --> 00:09:59,100
