139
00:10:17,220 --> 00:10:17,900
What about this?

140
00:10:18,420 --> 00:10:19,180
How can you explain it?

141
00:10:23,380 --> 00:10:24,580
It's not worth mentioning.

142
00:10:25,380 --> 00:10:26,820
No need to let it disturb you.

143
00:10:27,780 --> 00:10:28,980
It says in the letter that

144
00:10:28,980 --> 00:10:30,340
this is the fifth letter.

145
00:10:31,060 --> 00:10:32,020
No wonder that

146
00:10:32,020 --> 00:10:33,540
I can always smell the flavor of ink.

147
00:10:34,220 --> 00:10:36,020
You have burnt all the letters, right?

148
00:10:37,700 --> 00:10:38,300
It doesn't matter.

149
00:10:39,580 --> 00:10:40,780
I know what to do.

150
00:10:42,940 --> 00:10:44,140
The magic instrument that you asked him to make

151
00:10:44,260 --> 00:10:45,860
has come to the last stage.

152
00:10:46,300 --> 00:10:47,340
As for such masterly magic instrument,

153
00:10:47,460 --> 00:10:49,300
it is the most dangerous when it comes into being.

154
00:10:49,780 --> 00:10:51,140
If it can't be made successfully,

155
00:10:51,380 --> 00:10:53,340
all the efforts will be in vain.

156
00:10:53,420 --> 00:10:54,660
There may also be backfire.

157
00:10:55,100 --> 00:10:57,460
So you'd better go back quickly.

158
00:11:03,100 --> 00:11:04,380
As for Shen Ye...

159
00:11:04,500 --> 00:11:07,300
I know how to behave properly with Shen Ye.

160
00:11:07,700 --> 00:11:08,980
I'm sure to deal with him well.

161
00:11:12,100 --> 00:11:13,500
But I'll be out for a very long time.

162
00:11:13,900 --> 00:11:14,580
Very long?

163
00:11:16,140 --> 00:11:17,340
How long is it?

164
00:11:17,940 --> 00:11:18,740
Several months?

165
00:11:20,940 --> 00:11:21,820
Several years?

166
00:11:24,740 --> 00:11:25,220
Well...

167
00:11:26,940 --> 00:11:28,140
At least several days.

168
00:11:29,660 --> 00:11:30,380
It's just several days.

169
00:11:30,380 --> 00:11:32,220
You said as if you were away for a long time.

170
00:11:35,300 --> 00:11:37,300
Absence sharpens love.

171
00:11:39,460 --> 00:11:40,220
Isn't it long enough?

172
00:11:40,740 --> 00:11:41,380
How could you say that

173
00:11:41,820 --> 00:11:43,300
you were not good at talking?

174
00:11:57,140 --> 00:11:57,740
Your Highness.

175
00:11:57,860 --> 00:11:58,620
Your Excellency.

176
00:12:01,660 --> 00:12:02,420
What's wrong? Chacha.

177
00:12:02,540 --> 00:12:03,140
Tell me!

178
00:12:05,540 --> 00:12:07,100
Here is message from the palace that

179
00:12:07,580 --> 00:12:09,940
His Majesty and Her Majesty haven't seen you for a long time,

180
00:12:10,340 --> 00:12:11,220
so they asked you to go to the palace

181
00:12:11,740 --> 00:12:12,660
to relieve their lovesickness.

182
00:12:23,380 --> 00:12:24,740
I pay respects to father and mother!

183
00:12:25,180 --> 00:12:25,740
Rise!

184
00:12:26,100 --> 00:12:26,700
Thank you, father.

185
00:12:28,460 --> 00:12:29,500
How are you doing these days?

186
00:12:30,220 --> 00:12:32,100
Father, I'm fine.

187
00:12:35,020 --> 00:12:38,940
I heard that Lord Xi Ze had been living
in your mansion these days.

188
00:12:39,500 --> 00:12:42,420
How do you get on with each other?

189
00:12:44,060 --> 00:12:45,300
We get on peacefully

190
00:12:45,420 --> 00:12:47,140
with each other.

191
00:12:48,660 --> 00:12:49,500
It's good.

192
00:12:51,420 --> 00:12:53,700
Just peacefully?

193
00:12:55,580 --> 00:12:57,740
Rumor has it that

194
00:12:58,060 --> 00:13:00,100
Lord Xi Ze and you are closely attached to each other,

195
00:13:00,380 --> 00:13:01,780
which is very admiring.

196
00:13:02,580 --> 00:13:03,540
Mother,

197
00:13:04,140 --> 00:13:05,020
I did go out with Lord Xi Ze

198
00:13:05,180 --> 00:13:06,420
to the fair,

199
00:13:06,740 --> 00:13:08,940
but we didn't do anything that degraded
the decency of the imperial family.

200
00:13:10,340 --> 00:13:10,940
Never mind.

201
00:13:12,420 --> 00:13:14,820
Xi Ze used to be cold.

202
00:13:15,420 --> 00:13:16,860
Since he is kind to you,

203
00:13:17,700 --> 00:13:20,260
we feel very happy for you.

204
00:13:21,420 --> 00:13:23,380
Thank you for caring about me.

205
00:13:25,260 --> 00:13:27,580
If you don't have anything to say, you can leave now.

206
00:13:28,020 --> 00:13:28,420
OK.

207
00:13:30,540 --> 00:13:31,060
By the way,

208
00:13:32,980 --> 00:13:35,060
Shen Ye is making swords in your mansion, isn't he?

209
00:13:35,900 --> 00:13:37,380
How is it going?

210
00:13:38,700 --> 00:13:40,860
Though I don't know much about making swords,

211
00:13:41,460 --> 00:13:42,740
yet I have never heard

212
00:13:42,900 --> 00:13:44,220
he had any worries

213
00:13:44,340 --> 00:13:45,460
or troubles.

214
00:13:45,860 --> 00:13:46,780
So I think

215
00:13:46,820 --> 00:13:48,180
his work goes smoothly.

216
00:13:48,580 --> 00:13:49,980
You think it's smooth?

217
00:13:58,180 --> 00:14:00,940
Such important weapons are being forged in your mansion.

218
00:14:01,740 --> 00:14:04,140
Shouldn't you go to ask something about them?

219
00:14:04,540 --> 00:14:05,660
You're right, mother.

220
00:14:06,260 --> 00:14:08,180
I'm going back to see how it is going.

221
00:14:08,700 --> 00:14:09,380
Well,

222
00:14:10,700 --> 00:14:12,300
I can go back with her

223
00:14:12,620 --> 00:14:14,420
to see how it is going.

224
00:14:16,300 --> 00:14:17,220
Good.

225
00:14:18,020 --> 00:14:20,420
As mother and daughter, you hardly have chances
to talk with each other.

226
00:14:21,220 --> 00:14:21,700
Go ahead.

227
00:14:23,780 --> 00:14:25,220
Then you can have a talk with your father

228
00:14:25,620 --> 00:14:26,220
and wait for me for a while.

229
00:14:26,780 --> 00:14:27,180
I will.

230
00:14:43,580 --> 00:14:45,260
Mother, you know how to make swords, right?

231
00:14:47,180 --> 00:14:47,740
No.

232
00:14:48,900 --> 00:14:50,980
Could it be that you want to take the chance

233
00:14:51,140 --> 00:14:52,940
to talk something with me personally?

234
00:14:58,380 --> 00:15:00,420
Why did Xi Ze have a fancy for you suddenly?

235
00:15:01,820 --> 00:15:03,620
Mother, you are so strange.
How could you ask me such a question?

236
00:15:04,420 --> 00:15:06,100
Lord Xi Ze has been my husband for a long time.

237
00:15:06,700 --> 00:15:07,780
But I heard that

238
00:15:07,860 --> 00:15:10,620
Lord Xi Ze always lived on the Qi Nan Mountain.

239
00:15:11,820 --> 00:15:14,620
Your marriage just existed in the name only.

240
00:15:14,780 --> 00:15:15,300
Mother,

241
00:15:16,300 --> 00:15:17,860
those are just rumors.

242
00:15:18,460 --> 00:15:20,580
Lord Xi Ze and I are always attracted to each other.

243
00:15:21,340 --> 00:15:21,940
Could it be that

244
00:15:22,460 --> 00:15:24,460
you prefer to believe the slanders of the evil people

245
00:15:24,820 --> 00:15:26,340
rather than believe your daughter?

246
00:15:28,300 --> 00:15:29,180
How dare you talk to me like this?

247
00:15:29,940 --> 00:15:30,700
Please calm your anger, mother.

248
00:15:31,060 --> 00:15:32,900
I was just telling the truth.

249
00:15:33,660 --> 00:15:36,380
I'm wondering why you suddenly mentioned Xi Ze.

250
00:15:36,980 --> 00:15:39,540
Could it be that you are worried

251
00:15:40,340 --> 00:15:41,980
after hearing we love each other?

252
00:15:43,620 --> 00:15:45,820
Relying on Xi Ze's favor,

253
00:15:46,940 --> 00:15:48,940
you dare to talk with me like this.

254
00:15:49,820 --> 00:15:50,380
I dare not.

255
00:15:55,260 --> 00:15:56,740
Aranya's mother

256
00:15:57,860 --> 00:15:59,460
really hates her so much.

257
00:16:24,020 --> 00:16:24,460
Mother.

258
00:16:24,820 --> 00:16:26,020
Let me take you to the sword forging room.

259
00:16:26,700 --> 00:16:28,420
No need. I can go there myself.

260
00:16:35,180 --> 00:16:36,780
It's so strange today.

261
00:16:40,820 --> 00:16:43,060
Your Majesty, it's not a long time after your last visit.

262
00:16:44,340 --> 00:16:45,740
Aren't you afraid of His Majesty's suspicion?

263
00:16:47,620 --> 00:16:48,500
Don't worry.

264
00:16:49,100 --> 00:16:50,420
He allowed me to come here.

265
00:16:51,460 --> 00:16:52,740
I don't need to worry about anything.

266
00:16:53,540 --> 00:16:55,220
I'm not the one who is to rebel.

267
00:16:57,420 --> 00:16:58,380
Anyhow,

268
00:16:59,220 --> 00:17:00,860
I won't get you involved in it.

269
00:17:06,900 --> 00:17:09,660
You are not as calm as before.

270
00:17:14,180 --> 00:17:15,540
Today I come here

271
00:17:15,980 --> 00:17:17,500
to ask you again.

272
00:17:18,260 --> 00:17:19,700
If you'd like to join me,

273
00:17:20,340 --> 00:17:21,780
tell me your opinions.

274
00:17:22,860 --> 00:17:24,460
If not,

275
00:17:24,780 --> 00:17:25,820
just tell me directly.

276
00:17:27,300 --> 00:17:28,700
Even without you,

277
00:17:31,220 --> 00:17:32,580
I will still take actions.

278
00:17:52,220 --> 00:17:52,740
Your Highness.

279
00:17:55,300 --> 00:17:56,020
Your Highness.

280
00:18:00,060 --> 00:18:00,660
What's wrong?

281
00:18:00,900 --> 00:18:02,260
The steward said that

282
00:18:02,420 --> 00:18:04,740
Lord Shen Ye invited you to the Mengchun Courtyard.

